{"tid":1284433,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"支那小學生地鐵大聲自稱係狗","createTime":"2019-07-04T07:11:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T16:32:45.000Z","uid":169396,"like":92,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"aeca0693cebbcf6b0bc36a6b876e4b904044577b","tid":1284433,"uid":169396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T07:11:33.000Z","msg":"頭先坐地鐵隔離坐左一家三口，個小學生一上車就用支那話大叫大喊係咁講野。<br />\n<br />\n全車人嘖左幾下個老豆老母都淨係睇手機當冇事發生，本身已經忍無可忍諗住出聲叫佢細聲少少。<br />\n<br />\n佢突然間大叫：「（支那話）我是狗！我是狗！」然後大聲扮狗叫。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「汪汪汪汪汪汪」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你喺地鐵大大聲笑左出聲，對唔住我真係頂唔撚緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"145829fc3bc96bc2738199a6eb1922ab205180dc","tid":1284433,"uid":169396,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T07:12:37.000Z","msg":"我冇野講！汪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"159934fe01214cbaf0a48071c7fa1831ca7a4af2","tid":1284433,"uid":17472,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T07:12:54.000Z","msg":"0/10"},{"pid":"71ff3fb6ab2c78c79fc5231834a1e742300395d7","tid":1284433,"uid":89382,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T07:13:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c674ab05f2dcb0de5d1376ec574bfa58433a9530","tid":1284433,"uid":169396,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"159934fe01214cbaf0a48071c7fa1831ca7a4af2","tid":1284433,"uid":17472,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T07:12:54.000Z","msg":"0/10"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T07:14:34.000Z","msg":"真人真事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支那講事實又唔俾"},{"pid":"9c74d6201c46082ab454e892f7931ed43e1e5ca2","tid